nested_items.name: LongTermPricingEntries
nested_items.description: Each LongTermPricingEntry object contains a status, ID, and other information about the LongTermPricing type.

nested_items.name: LongTermPricingId
nested_items.description: The ID of the long-term pricing type for the device.

nested_items.name: LongTermPricingEndDate
nested_items.description: The end date the long-term pricing contract.

nested_items.name: LongTermPricingStartDate
nested_items.description: The start date of the long-term pricing contract.

nested_items.name: LongTermPricingType
nested_items.description: The type of long-term pricing that was selected for the device.

nested_items.name: CurrentActiveJob
nested_items.description: The current active jobs on the device the long-term pricing type.

nested_items.name: ReplacementJob
nested_items.description: A new device that replaces a device that is ordered with long-term pricing.

nested_items.name: IsLongTermPricingAutoRenew
nested_items.description: If set to true, specifies that the current long-term pricing type for the device should be automatically renewed before the long-term pricing contract expires.

nested_items.name: LongTermPricingStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the long-term pricing type.

nested_items.name: SnowballType
nested_items.description: The type of Snow Family devices associated with this long-term pricing job.

nested_items.name: JobIds
nested_items.description: The IDs of the jobs that are associated with a long-term pricing type.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: Because HTTP requests are stateless, this is the starting point for your next list of returned ListLongTermPricing list.
